{"tid":543074,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)奪寶奇兵1-4","createTime":"2018-01-28T06:27:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T10:01:47.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0279d024634c991c71bb61a91b33ee06882b3519","tid":543074,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T06:27:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=xl%2FLXOVrUJasthmZibJTJwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=69280fd5\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=xl%2FLXOVrUJasthmZibJTJwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=ff17424c\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/4b/Raiders.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F4b%2FRaiders.jpg&h=c4e52631&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.1936年，寶物獵人及考古學家印第安納&middot;瓊斯勇闖秘魯叢林，在充滿危險機關的古廟中尋找黃金神像。逃出古廟後，他卻遇見競爭對手：另一個考古學家瑞尼貝拉克以及他率領的土人，被迫交出他找到的金像。突破重圍後，印第安納&middot;瓊斯登上一艘早就安排好的水上飛機逃離了叢林。<br />\n<br />\n短暫停留美國後，他回到校園教授考古學。兩個陸軍情報人員到他的學校告訴他，德國納粹黨正在追求未知的神秘武力，並在追捕他的老師艾伯納瑞文伍德。瑞文伍德擁有稱為「拉雅之桿」頂端的元件<br />\n<br />\n2.1935年，考古學教授印第安納&middot;瓊斯帶著夜總會歌女威莉和12歲的孤兒小滑溜在中國上海一起逃命冒險，逃脫後意外到了一個破落的印度小村莊，這個小村落的所有幼童和村裡的3塊珍貴聖石都失蹤了。印第安納&middot;瓊斯承諾協助村長尋回失蹤的3塊珍貴聖石和兒童外，來到了盤踞邪惡勢力控制的王室宮殿，找出3塊具有神秘法力的寶石。印第安納&middot;瓊斯他們再度展開驚險的鬥智鬥力和奪寶追逐戰<br />\n<br />\n3.考古學教授印第安納&middot;瓊斯的父親亨利&middot;瓊斯教授，因為研究並尋找傳說中的耶穌聖杯而失蹤。由於德國納粹黨也要奪取有神奇力量的聖杯，印第安納&middot;瓊斯和父親必須在奧地利及德國納粹黨軍隊追殺下冒險死裡逃生。<br />\n<br />\n4.本片時代背景設置於《聖戰奇兵》的19年後，也就是1957年，而印第安納&middot;瓊斯博士則過著很平靜的生活，但是他隨後必須要對抗蘇聯幹員，爭奪水晶骷髏。故事設定水晶骷髏有可能是外星人或是古代馬雅文明所遺留。印第安納&middot;瓊斯博士的冒險則橫跨新墨西哥州、康乃狄克州、墨西哥市以及秘魯叢林。<br />\n<br />\n3 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=xl%2FLXOVrUJasthmZibJTJwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=8cf942d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=xl%2FLXOVrUJasthmZibJTJwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=3ac03864\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f247032a7bb5acfb18b18ce0d25ebd62eca62e42","tid":543074,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T06:29:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3afa365f0726fc7ee5cfa2b5834d5bb3c3919fa0","tid":543074,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T06:35:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23270c5d8b06f3fc53a4e5ad073415a64b351b72","tid":543074,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T06:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451f31099cdbe53f6965bc8a19a66ee249870cbd","tid":543074,